'''埃克索尔·罗斯'''（'''{{lang-en|Axl Rose}}'''，1962年2月6日－）原名'''威廉·布鲁斯·罗斯'''（William Bruce Rose, Jr.）；少年時稱'''威廉·布鲁斯·贝利'''（William Bruce Bailey）<ref>{{cite journal|title=Monitor|journal=Entertainment Weekly|date=Feb 8, 2013|issue=1245|page=22}}</ref>，[[美国|美国]][[摇滚樂|摇滚樂]]創作歌手和音樂家，是[[硬式摇滚|硬式摇滚]]樂團[[槍與玫瑰|槍與玫瑰]]的原始成員及主唱。出生在[[印第安纳州|印第安纳州]][[拉斐特_(印第安纳州)|拉斐特]]，他俱有[[苏格兰|苏格兰]]、[[爱尔兰|爱尔兰]]和[[德国|德国]]血统。由於他強勁的嗓音、廣濶的音域和充滿活力的現場表演，羅斯先後被各類媒體包括《[[滾石|滾石]]》和《[[新音樂快遞|新音樂快遞]]》評為有史以來最偉大的歌手之一。<ref>{{cite journal | last = Lethem | first = Jonathan | title = 100 Greatest Singers of All Time | journal = [[Rolling_Stone|Rolling Stone]] | date = 2008-11-27 | accessdate = 2011-06-03 | url = http://www.rollingstone.com/music/lists/100-greatest-singers-of-all-time-19691231/axl-rose-19691231 | archive-date = 2012-07-09 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120709154144/http://www.rollingstone.com/music/lists/100-greatest-singers-of-all-time-19691231/axl-rose-19691231 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal | title = Michael Jackson tops NME's Greatest Singers poll | journal = [[NME|NME]] | date = 2011-06-21 | accessdate = 2011-07-10 | url = http://www.nme.com/news/michael-jackson/57469 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110627082454/http://www.nme.com/news/michael-jackson/57469 | archivedate = 2011-06-27 | deadurl = no }}</ref>2016年起，除槍與玫瑰的活動外，他還兼任了澳洲搖滾樂團[[AC/DC|AC/DC]]的主唱<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/ac-dc-confirm-axl-rose-is-new-lead-singer-joining-band-on-tour-20160416|title=AC/DC Confirm Axl Rose Is New Lead Singer|publisher=[[滾石_(雜誌)|滾石 (雜誌)]]|date=2016-04-16|accessdate=2017-05-31|archive-date=2016-04-18|archive-url=https://archive.today/20160418020504/http://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/ac-dc-confirm-axl-rose-is-new-lead-singer-joining-band-on-tour-20160416|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==簡介==
===槍與玫瑰的形成===
埃克索尔·罗斯出生並成長於[[印第安纳州|印第安纳州]][[拉斐特_(印第安纳州)|拉斐特]]，父親老威廉·布魯斯·羅斯年僅二十歲，母親莎朗·林特納十六歲<ref name="watchyoubleed">{{cite book |last=Davis |first=Stephen |title=Watch You Bleed: The Saga of Guns N' Roses |year=2008 |publisher=Gotham Publishing |isbn=978-1-59240-377-6}}</ref>，在沒有預期下懷了孩子，他們在罗斯兩歲時離異。後來斯蒂芬·貝利成為埃克索尔的繼父，曾更改其姓氏為貝利。1980年代初罗斯搬到[[洛杉磯|洛杉磯]]，在那裡他成為活躍於當地的[[硬搖滾|硬搖滾]]現場表演藝人，並參與了幾支樂隊包括{{link-en|好萊塢玫瑰|Hollywood Rose}}和{{link-en|洛杉磯手槍|L.A. Guns}}（兩個樂團合併就是槍與玫瑰）。1986年3月他與[[格芬唱片公司|格芬唱片公司]]簽署合約前，正式把名字更改為埃克索尔·罗斯（W. Axl Rose）。<ref name="Sugerman91">{{cite book | last = Sugerman | first = Danny | title = Appetite for Destruction: The Days of Guns N' Roses | url = https://archive.org/details/appetitefordestr0000suge | publisher = St. Martin's Press | year = 1991 | isbn = 0-312-07634-7}}</ref>

===得到巨大成功===
1985年，他携手創辦[[槍與玫瑰|槍與玫瑰]]樂團，於1980年代末至1990年代初獲得巨大的成就和認同。樂團的第一張專輯《[[Appetite_for_Destruction|Appetite for Destruction]]》於1987年發布，至目前為止全球總銷量已超過3,000萬張<ref name=Smith>{{cite news| url=http://www.newsobserver.com/2012/11/19/2494907_american-masters-highlights-david.html| title='American Masters' highlights David Geffen's influence but only hints at a dark side| first=Sara| last=Smith| newspaper=The Kansas City Star| date=2012-11-18| accessdate=2014-03-11| archive-date=2014-03-09| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140309044138/http://www.newsobserver.com/2012/11/19/2494907_american-masters-highlights-david.html| dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=Havelock>{{cite journal| url=http://news.qthemusic.com/2012/08/column_-_still_hungry_25_years.html| title=Column - Still hungry? 25 years of Guns N' Roses' Appetite for Destruction| first=Laurie| last=Havelock| publisher=[[Q_magazine|Q magazine]]| date=2012-08-09| accessdate=2014-03-11| archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140311063307/http://news.qthemusic.com/2012/08/column_-_still_hungry_25_years.html| archivedate=2014-03-11| deadurl=yes| journal=}}</ref>。它亦是美國有史以來最暢銷的處女專輯，共有1,800萬張的銷量<ref name="RIAA Top 100">{{cite web | title = Top 100 Albums | publisher = Recording Industry Association of America | url = http://riaa.com/goldandplatinum.php?content_selector=top-100-albums | accessdate = December 18, 2011 | archive-date = 2011-06-04 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110604050421/http://www.riaa.com/goldandplatinum.php?content_selector=top-100-albums | dead-url = no }}</ref>，其中單曲《''Sweet Child o' Mine''》於1988年夏季打上美國排行榜冠軍位置。作為後續的雙專輯《[[Use_Your_Illusion_I|Use Your Illusion I]]》和《Use Your Illusion II》於1991年發布，得到廣泛的成功；它們先後打上[[告示牌排行榜|告示牌排行榜]]冠軍及亞軍位置，兩個專輯加起來在全球已售出3,500萬張。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://tsort.info/music/faq_album_sales.htm |title=Which albums had the highest number of worldwide sales? |accessdate=2012-03-14 |date=2007-12-15 |publisher=TSORT |archive-date=2012-03-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120327070348/http://tsort.info/music/faq_album_sales.htm |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

===樂團解體至現在===
1994年以後，著隨樂團歷時兩年半的「Use Your Illusion Tour」巡迴演唱會結束，羅斯從公共[[媒體|媒體]]中消失了好幾年，而樂團亦因為個人和音樂上的分歧而解體。作為唯一留下的創始成員，他繼續在[[槍與玫瑰|槍與玫瑰]]的旗幟下工作，因為他已經合法取得了樂團名字的擁有權。2001年元旦，他和[[槍與玫瑰|槍與玫瑰]]的全新陣容於[[拉斯維加斯|拉斯維加斯]]復出演唱，隨後預訂了定期的巡迴演出，以推廣準備發表的專輯《[[Chinese_Democracy|Chinese Democracy]]》，後來專輯拖延多年至2008年才推出市面。不過在商業上其銷量不及預期的好，儘管樂評人對該專輯多有正面的評價<ref name="AllMusic Biography">{{cite web | last = Erlewine | first = Stephen Thomas | title = Guns N' Roses Biography | publisher = AllMusic | url = http://www.allmusic.com/artist/guns-n-roses-p4416/biography | accessdate = December 18, 2011 | archive-date = 2011-09-03 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110903235655/http://www.allmusic.com/artist/guns-n-roses-p4416/biography | dead-url = no }}</ref>。2012年，羅斯以[[槍與玫瑰|槍與玫瑰]]成員的身份進入[[搖滾名人堂|搖滾名人堂]]，但他拒絕出席典禮活動，並要求個人從搖滾名人堂除名。

==健康問題==
26歲的時候羅斯被診斷患有[[躁鬱症|躁鬱症]]。雖然羅斯遵囑醫生吩咐服用鋰鹽，但他表示藥物對他效用不大，並聲稱他可以控制他的情緒<ref name="Tannenbaum88">{{cite journal | last = Tannenbaum | first = Rob | title = The Hard Truth About Guns N' Roses | journal = [[Rolling_Stone|Rolling Stone]] | date = 1988-11-17}}</ref>；羅斯曾在訪談中表示藥物並不能幫助他舒解壓力。1990年代初，羅斯成為[[順勢療法|順勢療法]]的堅定信徒，並定期接受「過去生活回憶治療」<ref name="RollingStone00">{{cite journal | title = What Happened to Axl Rose: The Inside Story of Rock's Most Famous Recluse | journal = [[Rolling_Stone|Rolling Stone]] | date = 2000-05-11 | accessdate = 2011-06-05 | url = http://www.heretodaygonetohell.com/articles/showarticle.php?articleid=32 | archive-date = 2011-09-06 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110906062814/http://www.heretodaygonetohell.com/articles/showarticle.php?articleid=32 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>。他分享了他受到親生父親[[性侵犯|性侵犯]]的往事，令到當時兩歲的他，曾經短暫停止了情感的成長<ref name="Neely92">{{cite journal | last = Neely | first = Kim | title = Axl Rose: The Rolling Stone Interview | journal = [[Rolling_Stone|Rolling Stone]] | date = 1992-04-02 | accessdate = 2011-06-03 | url = http://www.heretodaygonetohell.com/articles/showarticle.php?articleid=56 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110711163800/http://www.heretodaygonetohell.com/articles/showarticle.php?articleid=56 | archivedate = 2011-07-11 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。羅斯小時候與繼父同住，亦曾經遭受繼父[[暴力|暴力]]虐待。<ref name="RollingStoneBio">{{cite journal | title = Axl Rose: Biography | journal = [[Rolling_Stone|Rolling Stone]] | accessdate = 2011-06-06 | url = http://www.rollingstone.com/music/artists/axl-rose/biography | archive-date = 2017-12-06 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20171206005928/https://www.rollingstone.com/music/artists/axl-rose/biography | dead-url = no }}</ref>

